WEBVTT

00:00.534 --> 00:03.773
Green level floor lights will help guide you to the nearest exit.

00:04.279 --> 00:06.370
The exits are marked with amber lights.

00:06.800 --> 00:11.108
The safety card details the location and operation of the exit nearest you.

00:11.669 --> 00:13.564
Remember, it may be behind you.

00:14.150 --> 00:16.016
If you are seated behind row 11,...

00:16.300 --> 00:20.710
...there will be red arrows on top of the green floor level lights to direct you forward...

00:21.015 --> 00:23.473
...since there are no aft exits on the aircraft.

